OL,7,FA fraudster was jailed for three and a
OL,8,Fhalf years today, for conning high-
OL,9,Fprofile businesses into buying tea he
OL,10,Fclaimed was specially grown in
OL,11,FScotland, as ITV News Scotland
OL,12,FReporter Louise Scott explains
OL,14,FWords by ITV News Scotland Reporter
OL,15,FStephanie DochertyJA man has been
OL,16,Fjailed for three and a half years
OL,17,Fafter being found guilty of a tea
OL,18,Ffraud scheme, from which he earned
OL,19,Fover #500,000.
