OL,4,Chotels into buying his fake Scottish
OL,5,Ctea
OL,7,FThe tea menu at the Balmoral's Palm
OL,8,FCourt included names like Scottish
OL,9,FAntlers Tea and Highland Green and
OL,10,Fbased on descriptions Robinson gave
OL,11,Fthem, boasted "Our Scottish-grown teas
OL,12,Fcome from gardens in our farming
OL,13,Fheartlands in Perthshire and Dumfries
OL,14,Fand Galloway".
OL,16,FHe even claimed his Scottish tea was
OL,17,F"the Queen's favourite".
OL,19,FHe also defrauded a group of genuine
OL,20,FScottish tea growers by selling them
OL,21,Fplants under false pretences.
