OL,4,Chotels into buying his fake Scottish
OL,5,Ctea
OL,7,FOperating under the business name The
OL,8,FWee Tea Plantation, he pretended to
OL,9,Fcultivate unique Scottish tea plants
OL,10,Fon his Perthshire estate but
OL,11,Fprosecutors proved the product had
OL,12,Fbeen purchased elsewhere before being
OL,13,Frepackaged.
OL,15,FRobinson then fraudulently sold the
OL,16,Fplants to high-profile clients in the
OL,17,Fhospitality and retailers between
OL,18,FJanuary 2014 and February 2019 for
OL,19,Ffive times the cost.
