OL,7,FThe court heard he was importing the
OL,8,Fplants for three Euros each ` around
OL,9,F#2.50 - and collecting them from a
OL,10,Fmailbox in Glasgow and then selling
OL,11,Fthem for #12.50.
OL,13,FRobinson also fabricated his academic
OL,14,Fstatus by falsely claiming he had
OL,15,Fqualifications in agronomy and
OL,16,Fagriculture and had obtained awards
OL,17,Ffor his tea from industry bodies.
