OL,7,FHe was sentenced at Stirling Sheriff
OL,8,FCourt after a jury found him guilty of
OL,9,Ftwo charges of being concerned in a
OL,10,Ffraudulent scheme following an
OL,11,Finvestigation by Food Standards
OL,12,FScotland.
OL,14,FHe will now be subject to confiscation
OL,15,Fproceedings under Proceeds of Crime
OL,16,Flegislation to recover monies
OL,17,Fillegally obtained.
