OL,7,FRon McNaughton, Head of the Scottish
OL,8,FFood Crime and Incidents Unit (SFCIU)
OL,9,Fat Food Standards Scotland, said: "We
OL,10,Fwelcome today's sentencing as a clear
OL,11,Fsignal that food fraud is a serious
OL,12,Fcrime with serious consequences.
OL,14,F"A three-and-a-half year custodial
OL,15,Fsentence reflects the scale and impact
OL,16,Fof Mr Robinson's deception. His
OL,17,Factions caused real financial and
OL,18,Freputational harm to individuals,
OL,19,Fbusinesses and a developing sector of
OL,20,Fgenuine Scottish tea producers.
