OL,7,F"This outcome is the result of a
OL,8,Fcomplex and painstaking investigation
OL,9,Finvolving a dedicated team at FSS and
OL,10,Fthe cooperation of partner agencies
OL,11,Fand key witnesses.
OL,13,F"It demonstrates that those who set
OL,14,Fout to mislead consumers and defraud
OL,15,Fbusinesses will be held accountable.
