OL,7,F"Food fraud undermines consumer trust
OL,8,Fand damages the integrity of
OL,9,FScotland's globally respected food and
OL,10,Fdrink sector. We remain committed to
OL,11,Fdetecting and disrupting criminal
OL,12,Factivity of this nature."
OL,14,FHelen Nisbet, Procurator Fiscal for
OL,15,FTayside, Central and Fife, said: "This
OL,16,Fwas a planned and deliberate fraud.
OL,18,F"Thomas Robinson misled genuine
OL,19,FScottish tea growers by selling them
OL,20,Fplants he falsely claimed were a
OL,21,Funique, locally grown variety.
