OL,7,F"Fraud is not a victimless crime.
OL,8,FIndividuals, businesses, and genuine
OL,9,FScottish tea growers suffered
OL,10,Ffinancial and reputational harm as a
OL,11,Fconsequence of Robinson's deceit.
OL,13,F"But thanks to partnership working
OL,14,Fbetween Food Standards Scotland,
OL,15,FPolice Scotland and the Crown Office
OL,16,Fand Procurator Fiscal Service, he has
OL,17,Fbeen brought to account for his crimes.
OL,19,F"We are committed to tackling
OL,20,Ffinancial crime of this kind."
